        "action": "Require pubs and restaurants to close on Christmas Day so staff can celebrate",
        "additional_details": "Christmas is a family day and should be spent with families. There\u2019s more important things to life than working and money. I believe many staff of pubs and restaurants would much prefer to be at home Christmas Day. Some staff work every single day throughout the Christmas period without a day off.",
        "background": "The Government should require all hospitality venues to close on Christmas Day so staff can spend it with their families.",
